text: Salahuddin (born 2 November 1998) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 6 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
